title: Yarrrrrrctdoughbarrrrrchest: Blue Bayou with Captain Jason Barbosa aka Jason Sheridan, Michael Will Turner Carlson aka Mike Carlson, and Sauvignon Blanc Beard aka Scott Gairdner aka Podcast the Ride
itunes:title: Yarrrrrrctdoughbarrrrrchest: Blue Bayou with Captain Jason Barbosa aka Jason Sheridan, Michael Will Turner Carlson aka Mike Carlson, and Sauvignon Blanc Beard aka Scott Gairdner aka Podcast the Ride
description:
Jason Sheridan, Mike Carlson, and Scott Gairdner of Podcast: The Ride join the buckos to discuss their pirate names, favorite libations, and the Star Wars: Rise of the Resistance ride before wrapping up Yarrrchtdoughbarrrchest with a review of Disneyland's Blue Bayou. Plus, a new segment, Plank Check.

Sources for this week's intro:

http://kpolsson.com/disland/dl1966.html

https://www.mouseplanet.com/8202/The_Story_of_the_Red_Wagon_Inn

https://www.disneyfoodblog.com/the-disneyland-mobile-app-for-disneyland-resort-guests/
